    <mainBody>
      <level>
        <content>
          <p><b>Transposition Note for Directive (EU) 2015/2203 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 25 November 2015 on the approximation of the laws of the Member States relating to caseins and caseinates intended for human consumption (the “Directive”).</b></p>
        </content>
      </level>
      <paragraph>
        <content>
          <p>This Transposition Note sets out how the Directive is transposed in Scotland by the Caseins and Caseinates (Scotland) (No. 2) Regulations 2016 which revoke and replace The Caseins and Caseinates (Scotland) Regulations 1986 (as amended).</p>
          <table uk:widths="1.55in 2.46in 2.41in">
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p><b>Article</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Objective</b></p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p><b>Implementation</b></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 1</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Scope</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 3</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 2</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Definitions</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 2</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 3</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Obligations of Member states</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 4</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 4 (1)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Labelling</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 5(1) and Schedule 3</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 4 (2)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Appropriate language</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 5(2)</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 4(3)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Voluntary labelling</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 5(3) and Schedules 1, 2 and 3</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 5</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Delegation of power (to amend standards set out in Annexes I and II)</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Transposition not necessary</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 6</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Exercise of the delegation</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Transposition not necessary</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 7 </p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Transposition</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>The Regulations</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 8</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Repeal of Directive 83/417/EEC from 22 December 2016</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Transposition not necessary</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 9</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Entry into force</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulation 1</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Article 10</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Addresses</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Transposition not necessary</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Annex I, section I</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Standards applicable to edible acid caseins</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulations 4 and 5 and Schedule 1 </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Annex I, section II</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Standards applicable to edible rennet caseins</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulations 4 and 5 and Schedule 2</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Annex II</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Standards applicable to edible caseinates</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Regulations 4 and 5 and Schedule 3</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <p>Annex III</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Correlation table</p>
              </td>
              <td>
                <p>Transposition not necessary</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
